本前提。此外还包括高性能结构材料应用技术、快速测试发射技术、新型数字化技术、器箭一体化技术、电气一体化技术、高能煤油技术，这些将影响火箭的技术水平，是火箭方案先进性的重要体现。 同时，新一代载人运载火箭的研制探索了高效的运载火箭研发制造模式，将打造安全可靠、性能先进的载人运载火箭系列，除了载人月球探测，还能满足近地空间站后期运营需求。姜杰委员：新一代载人运载火箭或助力我国2030年载人登月"},"attached_info":"Cj4I+rrf4NX3u8NeEAMaCDc3ODY3ODQ1IP6Ji5EGMAA4K0Aocgk1MjAxMzc1MzB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"77 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-95266f5c00cf30288b09a5eb79b965bc_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"41_1646482440.8034048","card_id":"Q_520165894","target":{"id":520165894,"title":"好丽友使用的代可可脂到底是什么东西，对成人和孩子的健康危害大吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/520165894","type":"question","created":1646457684,"answer_count":26,"follower_count":35,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[361,15861,105508,121100,269055],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"近期，好丽友因为配料双标和使用代可可脂频频引人关注。这里面说到的代可可脂是什么东西，它和反式脂肪酸又是什么关系？对孩子和成年人的健康影响大吗？"},"attached_info":"Cj4I+rrf4NX3u8NeEAMaCDc3ODc0MTM5INTmi5EGMAA4I0Apcgk1MjAxNjU4OTR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"71 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-e8b57ddbec3cdf08edbad679fed3a99c_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"42_1646482440.8037481","card_id":"Q_64843570","target":{"id":64843570,"title":"高中三年需要切记和切忌什么？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/64843570","type":"question","created":1504429404,"answer_count":710,"follower_count":8829,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[119,1053,2029,4570,8220],"comment_count":14,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"准高一，想听听过来人的经验。"},"attached_info":"Cj4I+rrf4NX3u8NeEAMaCDE4MTYzODcyINyKr80FMA44/URAKnIINjQ4NDM1NzB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZ